a", "last_name": "Masson", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Bryan", "last_name": "Masson", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "K\u00e9vin", "last_name": "Mauvieux", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Nicolas", "last_name": "Meizonnet", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Pierre", "last_name": "Meurin", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Thibaut", "last_name": "Monnier", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Serge", "last_name": "Muller", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Jo\u00eblle", "last_name": "M\u00e9lin", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Ya\u00ebl", "last_name": "M\u00e9nach\u00e9", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Thomas", "last_name": "M\u00e9nag\u00e9", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Julien", "last_name": "Odoul", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Caroline", "last_name": "Parmentier", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Thierry", "last_name": "Perez", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "K\u00e9vin", "last_name": "Pfeffer", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Lisette", "last_name": "Pollet", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "St\u00e9phane", "last_name": "Rambaud", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Ang\u00e9lique", "last_name": "Ranc", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Julien", "last_name": "Rancoule", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Matthias", "last_name": "Renault", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Catherine", "last_name": "Rimbert", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Joseph", "last_name": "Rivi\u00e8re", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Laurence", "last_name": "Robert-Dehault", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "B\u00e9atrice", "last_name": "Roullaud", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Sophie-Laurence", "last_name": "Roy", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Ana\u00efs", "last_name": "Sabatini", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Alexandre", "last_name": "Sabatou", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Emeric", "last_name": "Salmon", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Anne", "last_name": "Sicard", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Emmanuel", "last_name": "Tach\u00e9 de la Pagerie", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Jean-Philippe", "last_name": "Tanguy", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Micha\u00ebl", "last_name": "Taverne", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Thierry", "last_name": "Tesson", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Lionel", "last_name": "Tivoli", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Romain", "last_name": "Tonussi", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Antoine", "last_name": "Villedieu", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric-Pierre", "last_name": "Vos", "party": "Rassemblement National"}, {"first_name": "Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric", "last_name": "Weber", "party": "Rassemblement National"}], "summary": "Par cet amendement, nous souhaitons aborder le retour des comp\u00e9tences \u00ab\u00a0eau\u00a0\u00bb et \u00ab\u00a0assainissement\u00a0\u00bb dans certains cas et de mani\u00e8re encadr\u00e9e.\nCette r\u00e9versibilit\u00e9 a toujours \u00e9t\u00e9 envisag\u00e9e lors des tentatives parlementaires visant \u00e0 att\u00e9nuer le transfert obligatoire vers les communaut\u00e9s de communes, obligation qui avait \u00e9t\u00e9 d\u00e9cid\u00e9e soudainement sans concertation ni \u00e9tude d\u2019impact.\nEn commission des lois, le sujet a \u00e9t\u00e9 abord\u00e9 au travers de divers amendements.\nNous estimons que le principe de libre administration des communes doit \u00eatre pleinement restaur\u00e9 et que les dispositions de la pr\u00e9sente loi ne peuvent \u00eatre que de simples \u00ab\u00a0assouplissements\u00a0\u00bb, mais doivent permettre de rendre aux communes les comp\u00e9tences dont elles s\u2019estiment l\u00e9s\u00e9es, qu\u2019elles ont parfois transf\u00e9r\u00e9es dans la pr\u00e9cipitation\u2026\nCette reprise de comp\u00e9tence doit n\u00e9anmoins \u00eatre conditionn\u00e9e et c\u2019est le sens de cet amendement.\nIl pr\u00e9voit que :\n1\u00b0 Seules les communaut\u00e9s de communes seront concern\u00e9es par le retour des comp\u00e9tences. En effet, il n\u2019est pas concevable d\u2019organiser ce retour dans les communaut\u00e9s d\u2019agglom\u00e9ration ou dans les m\u00e9tropoles.\n2\u00b0 L\u2019\u00e9ventuel retour des comp\u00e9tences est en outre envisageable par un vote conforme de la commune et de la communaut\u00e9 de commune auxquelles elles appartiennent.\n3\u00b0 Ce transfert ne serait en outre pas envisageable d\u00e8s lors\u00a0:\n\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 que toutes les communes d\u2019une communaut\u00e9 de communes ont d\u00e9j\u00e0 transf\u00e9r\u00e9 les comp\u00e9tences \u00ab\u00a0eau\u00a0\u00bb et \u00ab\u00a0assainissement\u00a0\u00bb ;\n\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 que des investissements importants sur les r\u00e9seaux d\u2019adduction et infrastructures d\u2019assainissement ont \u00e9t\u00e9 r\u00e9alis\u00e9s par la communaut\u00e9 de communes au profit de la commune qui solliciterait le retour des comp\u00e9tences et ne satisferait plus ainsi \u00e0 son devoir de solidarit\u00e9 r\u00e9ciproque.\nNous estimons en effet qu\u2019au sein d\u2019une communaut\u00e9 de commune si toutes les communes n\u2019ont pas transf\u00e9r\u00e9 leur comp\u00e9tence en eau et assainissement et si des investissements importants n\u2019ont pas \u00e9t\u00e9 r\u00e9alis\u00e9s, il est \u00e9quitable que la libert\u00e9 des communes s\u2019entende de ne pas transf\u00e9rer leurs comp\u00e9tences, mais aussi de pouvoir les r\u00e9cup\u00e9rer."}